I got an error when i use correlation tracker.
it appear there is missing include in the file `image_processing/correlation_tracker.h`.

the current included files
```
#include "correlation_tracker_abstract.h"
#include "../geometry.h"
#include "../matrix.h"
#include "../array2d.h"
